1
00:00:00,480 --> 00:00:04,480
[Exceptionally bright morning]

2
00:00:05,850 --> 00:00:08,750
[How's the morning
right before their final dates?]

3
00:00:09,020 --> 00:00:10,890
[Block C, Su Min's room]

4
00:00:17,060 --> 00:00:19,700
[Men's House]
[1F, Block A:
Yun Jae & Hyun Jun & Han Gyeol's room]

5
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:40,220
[2F, Block A:
Min Seong & Taichi's room]

6
00:00:45,620 --> 00:00:48,530
[Block B:
Hyeok Jin & Hyeong Jun & Sun Wook's room]

7
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,980
[Kim Sun Wook: Oh, what's going on?]

8
00:01:09,980 --> 00:01:12,550
[Kim Sun Wook:
You've pulled your bangs back.]

9
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:17,620
[Kim Sun Wook: Woah, ho, ho, ho.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You do it too.]

10
00:01:19,490 --> 00:01:21,360
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why can't I get it right?]

11
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:23,160
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I shouldn't use more spray, right?]

12
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:25,360
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes, it's enough.]

13
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:27,470
[Kim Sun Wook: You've used a lot of spray.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What?]

14
00:01:27,470 --> 00:01:29,430
[Kim Sun Wook: You've used a lot of spray.]

15
00:01:44,850 --> 00:01:46,450
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Time to get up.]

16
00:01:46,450 --> 00:01:49,650
[Oh Min Seong: What?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: We don't have much time left.]

17
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:56,590
[Oh Min Seong: Uh... OK...]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Still feeling unwell?]

18
00:01:59,259 --> 00:02:02,730
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You have to get up.]

19
00:02:02,730 --> 00:02:05,670
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who are you?]
[Oh Min Seong: When Taichi's done.]

20
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:08,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Get up.]

21
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:12,080
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Go wash up.]

22
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:15,980
[Coughs]

23
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:25,420
[Taichi: You pulled your bangs back?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What?]

24
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:27,890
[Taichi: You pulled your bangs back?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah, can't you see it?]

25
00:02:27,890 --> 00:02:31,300
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why?]
[Taichi: Nothing, just my first time seeing it.]

26
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:34,230
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
It's my first time doing it too.]

27
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,740
[Barely awake]

28
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:46,510
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
Here, cold medicine. Have it.]

29
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:51,579
[Oh Min Seong: What time is it?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Now? 10:40 AM.]

30
00:02:51,579 --> 00:02:53,520
[Oh Min Seong: What?]

31
00:02:54,790 --> 00:02:59,320
[Lee Hyeong Jun: 10 AM. One hour left.]

32
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,460
[Oh Min Seong: Ugh. It tastes yucky.]

33
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:09,270
[Oh Min Seong: I'll get ready quickly.]

34
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:12,670
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Come down after.]
[Oh Min Seong: OK.]

35
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:18,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: Where are you going?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I went to wake him up.]

36
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:20,150
[Lee Hyun Jun: He was still asleep?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

37
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:22,550
[Lee Hyun Jun: You pulled back your bangs?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Do I look weird?]

38
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:25,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: It suits you. It's nice.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Thank goodness.]

39
00:03:29,790 --> 00:03:32,960
[Kim Sun Wook: Did you sleep well?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

40
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: I heard you slept late.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hmm?]

41
00:03:35,890 --> 00:03:37,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: I heard you slept late.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Me? Yeah.]

42
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:39,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: Did you drink?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

43
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:43,430
[Kim Sun Wook: I drank beer.]

44
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,740
[Kim Sun Wook: Everyone was asleep.]

45
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:48,110
[Kim Sun Wook: Did you sleep right away?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

46
00:03:48,110 --> 00:03:50,780
[Kim Sun Wook: You must've been exhausted.]

47
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:05,260
[Lee Hyun Jun: What's wrong?]
[Kim Sun Wook: You're puffy.]

48
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:07,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: Am I?]
[Kim Sun Wook: A little.]

49
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:11,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: That's not good.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hehe.]

50
00:04:12,730 --> 00:04:14,330
[Kim Su Min: Hello.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hello.]

51
00:04:14,330 --> 00:04:17,269
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I came because I was bored.]
[Kim Su Min: Welcome.]

52
00:04:17,269 --> 00:04:21,910
[Kim Su Min: Do you feel better today?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm at a loss now.]

53
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:26,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Because what he said
was a clear rejection.]

54
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:30,150
[Kim Su Min: I heard a little about it.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: From whom?]

55
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:32,480
[Kim Su Min: Just here and there.]

56
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:35,150
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wanted to talk to him,
but I didn't get to,]

57
00:04:35,150 --> 00:04:37,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
so I kept wanting to talk to him,]

58
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:42,090
[Eum Hyeok Jin: which might've morphed into,
or I misinterpreted it, as attraction?]

59
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:45,030
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I also felt confused]

60
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:46,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: on the date yesterday,]

61
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:50,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
so there was a lot on my mind.]

62
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:53,970
[Kim Su Min: Apart from Han Gyeol,
is there anyone else you like?]

63
00:04:53,970 --> 00:04:57,510
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Well, honestly, rather than "like,"]

64
00:04:57,510 --> 00:05:01,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin: the one I wanted to talk to
was Min Seong.]

65
00:05:01,850 --> 00:05:05,050
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I was simply curious about him.]

66
00:05:05,050 --> 00:05:10,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But with how
things have developed, it's too late for me.]

67
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So go on a date with me.]

68
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I feel at ease with you.]

69
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:18,660
[Kim Su Min: Gosh, so many people
asking me out on a date.]

70
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:22,670
[Kim Su Min: Now that we're on the 6th day,
I've become so popular.]

71
00:05:22,670 --> 00:05:24,470
[Kim Su Min: I knew it.
It takes time for people to fall]

72
00:05:24,470 --> 00:05:25,870
[Kim Su Min: for my charms.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Totally.]

73
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:29,870
[Kim Su Min: All you short-sighted fools.]

74
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:32,540
[Kim Su Min: Unwise fools.]

75
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:37,350
[A morning where they want to
start something new]

76
00:05:40,290 --> 00:05:42,150
[Kim Su Min: It's actually the last day.]

77
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:48,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No. Tomorrow is the last day.]
[Kim Su Min: Didn't expect time to fly by.]

78
00:05:48,930 --> 00:05:53,360
[Kim Su Min:
Everyone's arriving one by one.]

79
00:05:56,030 --> 00:05:58,170
[Kim Su Min: Good morning.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Good morning.]

80
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:04,040
[Taichi: Hello.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hello.]

81
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,990
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What will we be doing?]

82
00:06:16,850 --> 00:06:23,260
[Heartfelt letters have been sent to you.
Please check the mailbox now.]

83
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:25,930
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Those mailboxes?]

84
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:33,400
[Heartfelt letters sent to the mailboxes]

85
00:06:33,710 --> 00:06:35,610
[Two days ago]

86
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:43,280
[Honest letters written
to the person they like]

87
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:51,290
[Heartfelt words written down on paper]

88
00:06:54,890 --> 00:07:01,170
[Have their hearts remained the same?]

89
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,310
[Kim Su Min: Go check it.]

90
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:18,340
[Kim Sun Wook]

91
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,430
[Kim Sun Wook: I received two letters.]

92
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:30,430
[Kim Sun Wook: First of all,
I was happy to see letters.]

93
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:33,460
[Kim Sun Wook: Even before reading them,
thinking about them]

94
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:37,200
[Kim Sun Wook: leaving the letters
in my mailbox, I can't help but find it cute.]

95
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:41,210
[Smiling at the sight of the letter]

96
00:07:41,659 --> 00:07:51,010
[To: Sun Wook. Seeing you laugh and having fun
during bowling today made me happy too.
I hope you keep having fun today, tomorrow,
and on the final day. For the remaining time,
let's have fun together! And talk more!]

97
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:51,020
[Kim Sun Wook: Su Min said he was happy
to spend a good time together.]

98
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:58,820
[Sun Wook, thanks for the gift and letter.
I was a teeny bit moved. If we get another
chance, let's go on another date here. Bye.]

99
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:55,690
[Kim Sun Wook: And Hyun Jun said
he was moved by my gift]

100
00:07:55,690 --> 00:07:58,820
[Kim Sun Wook:
and he wants to go on a date again.]

101
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,940
[Kim Sun Wook: I was happy.]

102
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,500
[Lee Hyun Jun:
I wanted to express my gratitude]

103
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,900
[Lee Hyun Jun:
and my feelings, so I wrote to him.]

104
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:07,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: Nothing's changed.]

105
00:08:07,570 --> 00:08:11,580
[Lee Hyun Jun: If anything,
my feelings for him are stronger.]

106
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:15,680
[Kim Su Min: He reacted differently
to the two letters.]

107
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:19,780
[Kim Su Min: For one of them, he looked giddy.]

108
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:21,420
[Kim Su Min: When he read my letter,]

109
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:25,760
[Kim Su Min: it was just a pleasant smile.]

110
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:29,360
[Kim Su Min:
If he were out of sight, I'd move on.]

111
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:32,600
[Kim Su Min: But he's always around here,
so it's hard.]

112
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:36,570
[Kim Su Min: I fall in love slowly.]

113
00:08:36,570 --> 00:08:40,500
[Kim Su Min: So, I think
I fall out of love slowly too.]

114
00:08:43,820 --> 00:08:44,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin]

115
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:58,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: When we were
told to write the notes,]

116
00:08:58,460 --> 00:09:00,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was chatting with him,]

117
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:01,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: then I went to the bathroom.]

118
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:03,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: Don't come in!
I'm writing the letter.]

119
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,010
[Kim Han Gyeol: But I'm almost done.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: OK.]

120
00:09:05,010 --> 00:09:06,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: Give me 30 seconds.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: OK, OK.]

121
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:08,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I didn't go in
and stayed on the sofa in Block A.]

122
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:11,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Then he suddenly
came out with the letter...]

123
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:13,640
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Is folding it like this too thick?]

124
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,810
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He didn't know
how to fold the letter.]

125
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:17,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I folded it for him.]

126
00:09:17,770 --> 00:09:22,110
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Based on that,
it was obvious that he wrote to me.]

127
00:09:22,110 --> 00:09:24,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It felt like
he wrote down his feelings]

128
00:09:24,850 --> 00:09:28,650
[Eum Hyeok Jin: after we had a chat.]

129
00:09:28,650 --> 00:09:29,790
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I knew I'd get a letter.]

130
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:33,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's the day
Hyeok Jin gave me Melona ice cream.]

131
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,230
[Kim Han Gyeol:
The ice cream was meaningful to us,]

132
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:38,830
[Kim Han Gyeol: and I also felt his care
as he waited to eat it with me,]

133
00:09:38,830 --> 00:09:41,630
[Kim Han Gyeol: so I wrote to him.]

134
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:44,970
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm a little sad because]

135
00:09:44,970 --> 00:09:47,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Han Gyeol's feelings
when he wrote the letter]

136
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:50,010
[Eum Hyeok Jin: are different from
his feelings when I received the letter.]

137
00:09:50,010 --> 00:09:53,480
[First, sorry for the ugly handwriting…
Thanks to your care and attention, I've gradually
grew fonder of you. It's charming that you are
sincere in every way, you've achieved a lot more
in life than me, and you're very mature.]

138
00:09:50,010 --> 00:09:51,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: And his last sentence]

139
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:54,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: about being charmed by my]

140
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:56,950
[If possible, I want to focus on you for
the rest of the stay. I hope you never ever
lose your intensity. Toodles.]

141
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:56,950
[Eum Hyeok Jin: maturity and achievements]

142
00:09:56,950 --> 00:10:01,650
[Eum Hyeok Jin: really stood out to me.]

143
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:05,660
[The past feelings that end with regret]

144
00:10:06,190 --> 00:10:08,130
[Kim Su Min: Go check your mailbox.]

145
00:10:10,190 --> 00:10:11,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hello.]
[Kim Su Min: Hello.]

146
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:13,530
[Cho Yun Jae: Hi.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why are your eyes so red?]

147
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:15,870
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know.]

148
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,640
[Lee Hyun Jun: I received two letters,]

149
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:29,750
[Lee Hyun Jun: from Yun Jae and Sun Wook.]

150
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:32,280
[Kim Sun Wook: Ah, I was the only one
who wrote my name.]

151
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:35,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What did you write?]
[Kim Sun Wook: My name.]

152
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:37,690
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wrote mine too.]

153
00:10:37,690 --> 00:10:40,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's funnier.]

154
00:10:42,490 --> 00:10:44,730
[Kim Sun Wook:
When I first wrote the letter,]

155
00:10:44,730 --> 00:10:48,630
[Kim Sun Wook: I pondered for a long time
how best I could express my sincerity,]

156
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:51,570
[Kim Sun Wook: so I kept editing it.]

157
00:10:51,570 --> 00:10:54,400
[Kim Sun Wook: I wrote it
while hoping my sincerity]

158
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,910
[Kim Sun Wook: is well conveyed.]

159
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:01,110
[Cho Yun Jae: When I wrote the letter,]

160
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:04,980
[Cho Yun Jae: I thought
I'd like Hyun Jun until the end.]

161
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:11,160
[Cho Yun Jae: So I wrote to him
to express those feelings.]

162
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:15,360
[Did their feelings reach Hyun Jun?]

163
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:20,800
[Lee Hyun Jun: Simply put, (Sun Wook's) letter
was about how he likes me a lot.]

164
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:18,990
[To: Hyun Jun-hyung. Today's group date was
new and fun. Though of course I kept looking
at you, hehe. Do you know you're very cute
when you bowl? How could you be so cute?]

165
00:11:18,990 --> 00:11:20,800
[And you have a really pretty smile. You say
you don't smile a lot, but seeing you smile
and having fun made me happy. From now on,
I'll keep making you smile. -Sun Wook]

166
00:11:21,190 --> 00:11:22,710
[To: Hyun Jun. Hello? Hehe. I'm Yun Jae. Now I'm
getting used to this and have gotten close with
many people. I think it's thanks to you too.
Thanks for taking care of me from the first day!]

167
00:11:22,710 --> 00:11:24,230
[We were really awkward when we first met, hehe.
I don't know why, but you were
my number one from the moment we met,
and my feelings haven't changed.]

168
00:11:23,170 --> 00:11:27,270
[Lee Hyun Jun: Reading Yun Jae's letter
left me with a heavy heart.]

169
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:27,260
[Sometimes I wonder if I should be more proactive,
but this is who I am. I want to approach you
and get closer gradually, with honest and sincere
feelings rather than swift and frivolous feelings!
Don't know if it works to my advantage, but I'll
keep taking it slow. I still like you a lot!]

170
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:29,410
[Lee Hyun Jun: He liked me a lot,]

171
00:11:29,410 --> 00:11:33,710
[Lee Hyun Jun: but he ended up with
nothing but hurt from me.]

172
00:11:33,710 --> 00:11:35,480
[Lee Hyun Jun: What stood out to me]

173
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:39,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: for both letters was
them telling me that they like me a lot.]

174
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:58,040
[Kim Han Gyeol: I received one letter.]

175
00:11:58,570 --> 00:12:01,640
[Kim Han Gyeol: "I'm clumsy
in relationships, but I'll try my best."]

176
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:04,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: He made it clear]

177
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:08,550
[Kim Han Gyeol: in a long letter
filled with warm words.]

178
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:11,650
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was really conflicted.]

179
00:12:11,650 --> 00:12:14,590
[Kim Han Gyeol: And I didn't expect
to receive a letter at that time.]

180
00:12:14,590 --> 00:12:18,390
[Kim Han Gyeol:
So there was a lot on my mind.]

181
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:27,230
[Cho Yun Jae: I got one letter.]

182
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:30,530
[Cho Yun Jae: I think it's from Taichi.]

183
00:12:30,530 --> 00:12:32,970
[Cho Yun Jae: Taichi always told me]

184
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:36,810
[Cho Yun Jae: he's very picky
and overthinks things.]

185
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:36,810
[To: Yun Jae-hyung. We haven't talked much,
but talking with you is always fun]

186
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:42,710
[and we share the same sense of humor.
I want to get closer to you.
-Someone who wants to get closer to you]

187
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:40,280
[Cho Yun Jae:
And that chats with me were effortless,]

188
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:42,710
[Cho Yun Jae:
and he's never felt that way before.]

189
00:12:42,710 --> 00:12:47,150
[Cho Yun Jae: I think Taichi
wanted to get close to me,]

190
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:49,020
[Cho Yun Jae: so my guess was Taichi.]

191
00:12:55,090 --> 00:12:58,100
[Taichi: Not checking your mail?]

192
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:05,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun]

193
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:13,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
There was one letter in the mailbox.]

194
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:17,310
[Lee Hyeong Jun: When I opened it,
I saw that it was from Min Seong.]

195
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:21,320
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He wrote a lot,]

196
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:21,320
[To: Hyeong Jun. Today's date was really fun and
heart-fluttering. Yesterday was a tough day, but I
hope you had a good day today. I really had a
good day… Thank you for telling me how you feel.
I was really angry and frustrated yesterday,]

197
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:25,890
