00:24:14,300 --> 00:24:16,030
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really? That's good.]

402
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:18,550
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You got five votes.
I was so surprised.]

403
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:21,070
[Oh Min Seong: Now it feels
I'm above your league, right?]

404
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:22,570
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Me?]
[Oh Min Seong: Me.]

405
00:24:22,570 --> 00:24:25,010
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why?]
[Oh Min Seong: I got five votes.]

406
00:24:25,010 --> 00:24:30,050
[Oh Min Seong: My sincerity
touched everyone. Don't you think?]

407
00:24:30,850 --> 00:24:35,650
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That's a different matter.]

408
00:24:35,650 --> 00:24:40,290
[Lee Hyeong Jun: How are you feeling?]
[Oh Min Seong: I'm fine.]

409
00:24:40,290 --> 00:24:41,560
[Oh Min Seong: No, I'm not feeling well.]

410
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:43,930
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah, I'm dying.]

411
00:24:43,930 --> 00:24:47,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You won't die.]
[Oh Min Seong: I'm in so much pain.]

412
00:24:47,460 --> 00:24:51,970
[Oh Min Seong: So much pain.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No, you're fine.]

413
00:24:55,670 --> 00:24:58,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Taken your medicine?]
[Oh Min Seong: I just took it.]

414
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,480
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Which?]
[Oh Min Seong: The one you gave me.]

415
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:02,510
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That's not enough.
Have a Strepsils lozenge.]

416
00:25:02,510 --> 00:25:03,950
[Oh Min Seong:
I have more medicine over there.]

417
00:25:03,950 --> 00:25:06,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Found it.]

418
00:25:18,900 --> 00:25:22,370
[Oh Min Seong:
What kind of date will I have today?]

419
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:26,300
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Your Super Date?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

420
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:28,940
[Oh Min Seong: You don't know what it is, right?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Of course not.]

421
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:34,380
[Oh Min Seong: A date with two people.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Gasps. With two people?]

422
00:25:35,010 --> 00:25:38,980
[Oh Min Seong: One is you.
And another person.]

423
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:41,320
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who did you choose?]

424
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:43,720
[Oh Min Seong: I'm not telling you.]

425
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:47,760
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who did you choose?
Why won't you tell me?]

426
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:50,530
[Oh Min Seong: It's a secret.
They said to keep it a secret.]

427
00:25:50,530 --> 00:25:53,860
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's a secret?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah, I can't tell anyone.]

428
00:25:53,860 --> 00:25:57,600
[Lee Hyeong Jun: How'd you decide?]
[Oh Min Seong: How?]

429
00:25:57,600 --> 00:26:01,580
[Oh Min Seong: Just... someone
I want to date other than you.]

430
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:02,970
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I see.]

431
00:26:02,970 --> 00:26:06,810
[Oh Min Seong: Someone I'm comfortable with.
You're the one I like.]

432
00:26:06,810 --> 00:26:10,150
[Oh Min Seong: You're who I like.
He's just someone I'm comfortable with.]

433
00:26:10,150 --> 00:26:13,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Just say
you can't go on the other date.]

434
00:26:13,620 --> 00:26:15,020
[Oh Min Seong: Refuse the other date?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

435
00:26:15,020 --> 00:26:18,320
[Oh Min Seong: Can't I write
the same person for both?]

436
00:26:18,320 --> 00:26:19,620
[Oh Min Seong: I doubt I can, right?]

437
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:24,730
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Nothing's impossible.
Screw them.]

438
00:26:24,730 --> 00:26:27,400
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Want a gift?]
[Oh Min Seong: What is it?]

439
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:36,910
[Oh Min Seong: You have
a star one and a heart one?]

440
00:26:36,910 --> 00:26:40,380
[Oh Min Seong: I should hang it.
Where should I hang it?]

441
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:42,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I was
going to give it to you at the end.]

442
00:26:42,780 --> 00:26:44,510
[Oh Min Seong: Really?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But since you]

443
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:46,250
[Lee Hyeong Jun: mentioned two dates...]

444
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:50,790
[Lee Hyeong Jun: See you later.]
[Oh Min Seong: OK.]

445
00:26:54,260 --> 00:26:56,930
[Who's the first man
to prepare for his last date is?]

446
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:26,020
[A place full of sweet and savory smells]

447
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:34,030
[What words will they use
to convey their feelings?]

448
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:45,540
[Who is Min Seong's first date?]

449
00:27:45,700 --> 00:27:49,700
[Ah, why am I getting nervous?]

450
00:27:49,700 --> 00:27:51,780
[I can do well, right?]

451
00:28:02,500 --> 00:28:05,970
[Taichi: Hello.]
[Oh Min Seong: Hello.]

452
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:09,900
[Oh Min Seong: Why is he here?]

453
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:13,180
[Oh Min Seong: I didn't expect it at all.]

454
00:28:13,710 --> 00:28:17,180
[Taichi: Did you expect me?]
[Oh Min Seong: No, how could I?]

455
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:19,590
[Taichi: Right?]

456
00:28:21,020 --> 00:28:22,500
[Oh Min Seong: Why are you here?]

457
00:28:22,500 --> 00:28:25,380
[Oh Min Seong: Did you choose me?
[Taichi: Yes, I did.]

458
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:28,280
[Oh Min Seong: What did you choose me for?]
[Taichi: Well...]

459
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:30,990
[Taichi: I chose Min Seong because]

460
00:28:30,990 --> 00:28:33,320
[Taichi: when I thought about]

461
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:36,160
[Taichi: who I'm curious about
after ending things with Han Gyeol,]

462
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:38,660
[Taichi: the first person I thought of
was Min Seong.]

463
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:41,300
[Taichi: In the seven days I've been here,]

464
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:45,940
[Taichi: my heart has only fluttered
for Min Seong.]

465
00:28:46,470 --> 00:28:50,470
[Taichi: I really
wanted to call you that day.]

466
00:28:50,470 --> 00:28:52,340
[Taichi: I was really going to call you.]

467
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:55,910
[Taichi: But you kept telling me not to.]
[Oh Min Seong: No, I was...]

468
00:28:55,910 --> 00:28:59,720
[Oh Min Seong: really just kidding.
I don't usually do that, right?]

469
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:02,750
[Oh Min Seong: But I was joking
when I asked you not to call me.]

470
00:29:02,750 --> 00:29:06,290
[Taichi: I wanted to call you
and go on a date with you.]

471
00:29:06,290 --> 00:29:08,890
[Taichi: I think rooming together
played a big part.]

472
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:11,160
[Taichi: On your first day,
we went on a date.]

473
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:13,300
[Taichi: After our date, I was actually]

474
00:29:13,300 --> 00:29:15,570
[Taichi: worried about sharing a room.]

475
00:29:15,570 --> 00:29:17,200
[Taichi: That I had to room with you alone.]

476
00:29:17,770 --> 00:29:21,990
[Taichi: I was worried, but once we started
rooming together, I actually enjoyed it.]

477
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,840
[Oh Min Seong: Has it been OK?]
[Taichi: Yes, really.]

478
00:29:23,840 --> 00:29:25,710
[Taichi: It's been really fun.]

479
00:29:25,710 --> 00:29:27,040
[Taichi: It was unexpected,]

480
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:28,910
[Taichi: so I wanted to call you that day.]

481
00:29:28,910 --> 00:29:31,850
[Taichi: But you kept telling me not to.]

482
00:29:31,850 --> 00:29:34,520
[Taichi: So I didn't call you.]
[Oh Min Seong: I was kidding.]

483
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:37,050
[Oh Min Seong: The thought of him calling me
never crossed my mind.]

484
00:29:37,050 --> 00:29:40,390
[Oh Min Seong: I was totally joking
when I told him not to call me.]

485
00:29:40,390 --> 00:29:45,730
[Oh Min Seong: When I found out,
I was a bit stumped.]

486
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:48,100
[Taichi:  Want to try it?]
[Oh Min Seong: Want me to cut it for you?]

487
00:29:48,100 --> 00:29:50,000
[Oh Min Seong: Do you like Mont Blanc bread?]

488
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,870
[Taichi: Yes.]
[Oh Min Seong: Can it be cut?]

489
00:29:52,670 --> 00:29:54,100
[Taichi: I'm curious about something.]

490
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:59,610
[Taichi: Why'd you choose me
for the first date and as a roommate?]

491
00:30:00,010 --> 00:30:03,310
[Oh Min Seong: Because you're handsome.]

492
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:05,310
Because you're handsome.

493
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:08,950
[Taichi: But I found you handsome after time.]
[Oh Min Seong: Don't lie.]

494
00:30:08,950 --> 00:30:12,150
[Taichi: Really. When I first met you,]

495
00:30:12,150 --> 00:30:15,290
[Taichi: I wasn't like attracted to you.]

496
00:30:12,460 --> 00:30:14,260
Didn't find me handsome?

497
00:30:15,290 --> 00:30:19,820
[Taichi: But... When was it?
The third or fourth day rooming together,]

498
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:23,900
[Taichi: when your bangs were down
after taking a shower.]

499
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:27,460
[Taichi: With wet hair, I suddenly
thought you were good looking.]

500
00:30:27,700 --> 00:30:28,500
Really?

501
00:30:28,020 --> 00:30:31,700
[Oh Min Seong: You just like the bangs look.]
[Taichi: Is that it?]

502
00:30:31,910 --> 00:30:34,910
[Taichi: But I think
you look good without makeup.]

503
00:30:34,910 --> 00:30:36,180
[Oh Min Seong: I look better without makeup?]
[Taichi: Yes.]

504
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:40,750
[Oh Min Seong: Should I stop putting on makeup?]
[Taichi: That's fine too.]

505
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:42,870
[Oh Min Seong:
You're always handsome. I'm envious.]

506
00:30:42,870 --> 00:30:44,990
[Taichi: No. You're handsome too.]

507
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:48,720
[Oh Min Seong: So what's on your mind now?]

508
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:50,590
[Oh Min Seong: No one you like at all?]

509
00:30:51,660 --> 00:30:54,600
[Taichi: I don't really have one now.]
[Oh Min Seong: Not really?]

510
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:58,600
[Taichi: I sorta know how you feel, though.]
[Oh Min Seong: How do I feel?]

511
00:30:58,870 --> 00:31:02,610
[Taichi: Isn't it Hyeong Jun?]
[Oh Min Seong: It's you.]

512
00:31:02,610 --> 00:31:04,770
[Taichi: Don't lie.]

513
00:31:04,770 --> 00:31:06,080
[Oh Min Seong: It's you.]

514
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:09,810
[Spent their first night back-to-back
because of awkwardness]

515
00:31:10,610 --> 00:31:14,350
[In a blink of an eye,
they're sleeping face-to-face with bed hair]

516
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:24,290
[Oh Min Seong: I'm rooting for you.
You're a good kid. You'll meet a good person.]

517
00:31:24,290 --> 00:31:27,960
[Oh Min Seong: It's normal that you didn't
meet someone you like here, since there]

518
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:30,430
[Oh Min Seong: aren't many to choose from.]
[Taichi: Yeah.]

519
00:31:30,430 --> 00:31:35,440
[Oh Min Seong: You can
meet good people outside too.]

520
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:33,140
Yes.

521
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:39,610
[Taichi: When voting for the best fit today,
I really chose you.]

522
00:31:39,610 --> 00:31:43,610
[Taichi: Because after getting here,
I think you were the most honest]

523
00:31:43,610 --> 00:31:49,520
[Taichi: and forward one. It was really cool.]
[Oh Min Seong: It's great you think it's cool.]

524
00:31:49,950 --> 00:31:53,860
[Taichi: I think you integrated well here.]
[Oh Min Seong: Really? Thank you.]

525
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,790
[Oh Min Seong: I hope
your remaining time here is enjoyable.]

526
00:31:56,790 --> 00:32:01,600
[Oh Min Seong: Though there's only one day left,
today and tomorrow are both important.]

527
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:06,400
[Taichi: Before I came in here today,
I was the most nervous I've been.]

528
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:12,270
[Oh Min Seong: Why? Before you came in here?]
[Taichi: At the stairs outside.]

529
00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:12,580
I thought...

530
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:16,550
[Taichi: This might be
the most proper date I'd have.]

531
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:20,020
[Oh Min Seong: But it's so short.]
[Taichi: Yeah, it's a pity.]

532
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:23,220
[Taichi: Too short to show my charms.]
[Oh Min Seong: What are your charms?]

533
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:25,090
[Taichi: I have a lot of charms.]

534
00:32:25,090 --> 00:32:27,520
[Taichi: I want to show them all,
but there's no time.]

535
00:32:27,520 --> 00:32:29,360
[Oh Min Seong: No time?]

536
00:32:29,360 --> 00:32:34,230
[Taichi: It's also fun dating me.]
[Oh Min Seong: I see. Appealing again, huh?]

537
00:32:34,230 --> 00:32:37,630
[Taichi: Of course. It's a date after all.]

538
00:32:37,630 --> 00:32:43,510
[Taichi: I'm so nervous that it's flying by.
I don't even remember what I've said.]

539
00:32:43,510 --> 00:32:46,440
[Taichi: But I'm happy to
get a last chance like this.]

540
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:48,580
[Oh Min Seong: If I knew you were coming,
I should've come with wet hair.]

541
00:32:49,910 --> 00:32:52,580
[Taichi: You with wet hair
did make my heart flutter.]

542
00:32:54,250 --> 00:32:56,590
[Oh Min Seong: Thank you.]

543
00:32:56,590 --> 00:32:59,620
[Oh Min Seong: He chose me anyway.]

544
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:02,860
[Oh Min Seong:
So I didn't have to be uneasy.]

545
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:07,260
[Oh Min Seong: I just
wanted to help him be relaxed.]

546
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:11,530
[Taichi: At this point, it's not like I think
I could change Min Seong's mind.]

547
00:33:11,530 --> 00:33:12,730
[Taichi: And I didn't]

548
00:33:12,730 --> 00:33:14,640
[Taichi: want to do that either.]

549
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:17,940
[Taichi:
But I couldn't help but feel excited.]

550
00:33:17,940 --> 00:33:22,480
[Taichi: So I regret
not making the call early on.]

551
00:33:23,010 --> 00:33:24,880
[Taichi: I regret that.]

552
00:33:25,410 --> 00:33:26,480
[Oh Min Seong: Take care.]
[Taichi: I had fun.]

553
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:30,750
[Oh Min Seong: Me too. Bye.]
[Taichi: Good luck.]

554
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:35,780
[The double-room roommates end the date
with mutual encouragement]

555
00:33:35,780 --> 00:33:39,460
[Café 109
Botanical Garden]

556
00:33:39,830 --> 00:33:43,300
[Someone is headed toward the date location
full of greenery]

557
00:33:56,910 --> 00:34:01,720
[Who is the date
that's making Han Gyeol nervous?]

558
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:10,530
[Eum Hyeok Jin: There was only
one person I wanted to choose.]

559
00:34:10,530 --> 00:34:13,199
[Eum Hyeok Jin: In case
there were things I haven't said]

560
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:15,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
due to worries and confusion,]

561
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:19,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: to tell them all to him
and leave no regret, I chose him.]

562
00:34:24,139 --> 00:34:28,409
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hello.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's nice.]

563
00:34:28,219 --> 00:34:28,880
This smell.

564
00:34:30,179 --> 00:34:32,409
[Kim Han Gyeol:
It smells like grass. It's nice.]

565
00:34:33,219 --> 00:34:37,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I just wanted to see him.]

566
00:34:37,250 --> 00:34:42,159
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I wasn't sure what to say first.]

567
00:34:42,159 --> 00:34:48,159
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Han Gyeol looked flustered,
like he didn't expect me to show up.]

568
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:54,139
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't expect
Hyeok Jin to show up.]

569
00:34:54,139 --> 00:34:59,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: So when I saw him,
I was kinda at a loss.]

570
00:35:06,850 --> 00:35:09,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What were you doing?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Me?]

571
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:14,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: Just waiting in the cafe.]

572
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:17,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Did you know I was coming?
You should've known, right?]

573
00:35:17,930 --> 00:35:19,830
[Kim Han Gyeol: I...]

574
00:35:19,830 --> 00:35:23,670
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't expect it.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Oh, really?]

575
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:30,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It'd be funny
for me to choose anyone else.]

576
00:35:30,220 --> 00:35:32,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Just...]

577
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:36,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin: By my standards,
you were my only choice.]

578
00:35:38,510 --> 00:35:41,550
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's why I chose you.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I see.]

579
00:35:45,290 --> 00:35:49,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: If I were you,
I probably wouldn't have chosen me.]

580
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:52,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why?]

581
00:35:52,230 --> 00:35:54,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: No?]

582
00:35:55,160 --> 00:35:59,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Well, I usually...]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah?]

583
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:02,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Go all out
so as not to leave regrets.]

584
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:07,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I just don't want any regrets.]

585
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:13,050
[Eum Hyeok Jin: This morning,
I received the note. The letter.]

586
00:36:13,650 --> 00:36:19,890
[Eum Hyeok Jin: From my point of view,
it really hurt.]

587
00:36:19,890 --> 00:36:25,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Because my charms
that you wrote about]

588
00:36:26,130 --> 00:36:31,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and why you rejected me
are the same.]

589
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That kinda hurt.]

590
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:37,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: In just a day, how different
you felt when sending the letter]

591
00:36:37,870 --> 00:36:42,410
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and when you rejected me
also hurt.]

592
00:36:45,350 --> 00:36:49,350
[Kim Han Gyeol:
But what I want to tell you is...]

593
00:36:50,350 --> 00:36:57,530
[I think I'm learning
how to be loved from you.]

594
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:55,020
Learn what?

595
00:36:57,530 --> 00:37:01,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know
how to be loved either.]

596
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:08,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I always
approach others and fall in love first.]

597
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:10,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm clumsy in love too.]

598
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:16,050
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's why I also asked you
to tell me if you felt pressured.]

599
00:37:16,050 --> 00:37:18,110
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's because...]

600
00:37:18,110 --> 00:37:24,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm not good at telling
when others feel pressured.]

601
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:27,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Because I'm not good at love.]

602
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:30,730
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I prefer to
hear it from them directly.]

603
00:37:36,330 --> 00:37:38,730
[Kim Han Gyeol: If I have to define it
based on whether I was at ease or not,]

604
00:37:38,730 --> 00:37:41,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: of course I wasn't at ease,
from my point of view.]

605
00:37:41,940 --> 00:37:46,410
[Kim Han Gyeol: But to me,
Hyeok Jin looked very at ease]

606
00:37:46,410 --> 00:37:49,410
[Kim Han Gyeol: and unwavering.]

607
00:37:50,310 --> 00:37:55,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I always liked others first.]

608
00:37:55,820 --> 00:38:00,090
[Eum Hyeok Jin: When people who liked me
approached me,]

609
00:38:00,090 --> 00:38:03,930
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think I acted just like you,
come to think of it.]

610
00:38:03,930 --> 00:38:07,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Since I'm not used to being loved.]

611
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:12,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's normal. It's the same.]

612
00:38:12,770 --> 00:38:17,610
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's what I think.
When I first met you here,]

613
00:38:17,610 --> 00:38:22,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: you looked like someone
who took the initiative to give love.]

614
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:27,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's why
I'm more attracted to you.]

615
00:38:27,250 --> 00:38:31,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Since we might be similar,
being the one who takes the initiative.]

616
00:38:31,620 --> 00:38:35,790
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So when we got closer,]

617
00:38:35,790 --> 00:38:40,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I thought you could
accept and understand me.]

618
00:38:41,460 --> 00:38:44,130
[Eum Hyeok Jin: From your point of view,]

619
00:38:44,130 --> 00:38:46,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin: being honest upfront]

620
00:38:46,230 --> 00:38:49,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: is being considerate of me,]

621
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:52,570
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but from my point of view,
it was too soon.]

622
00:38:52,570 --> 00:38:55,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Those words were]

623
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:59,750
[Eum Hyeok Jin: too heavy for me to bear.]

624
00:38:59,950 --> 00:39:04,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I thought it might've been
better if you'd told me later]

625
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:07,690
[Eum Hyeok Jin: or told me the next day.]

626
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:21,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's why I showed you
a side of me you'd never seen,]

627
00:39:21,770 --> 00:39:24,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: which I]

628
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:29,610
[Eum Hyeok Jin: really didn't want to show.
But I ended up falling apart.]

629
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:35,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I didn't have the energy
to think about how I appeared to you.]

630
00:39:36,220 --> 00:39:41,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think
that was what it was. I regret it now.]

631
00:39:43,390 --> 00:39:46,090
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's so hard, isn't it?]

632
00:39:48,200 --> 00:39:50,330
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

633
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:57,270
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So actually...]

634
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:04,750
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It'd be harder for me
to keep these, so...]

635
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:10,890
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Your photos,
and the photos we took together.]

636
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:18,890
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm not
giving them to you to cut ties.]

637
00:40:18,890 --> 00:40:24,530
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I just feel like
I'd be more confused if I kept them.]

638
00:40:24,900 --> 00:40:29,500
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Even so, in this situation,]

639
00:40:29,500 --> 00:40:36,510
[Eum Hyeok Jin: what I want to say
and what I can give you are that...]

640
00:40:36,750 --> 00:40:41,550
[I was sure it was you
from start to finish.]

641
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:48,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Since I was rejected,
I have to sort out my emotions.]

642
00:40:49,390 --> 00:40:54,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't think
I can let it go easily,]

643
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:58,570
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I thought of
returning them to him.]

644
00:40:58,670 --> 00:41:01,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: And also,]

645
00:41:01,770 --> 00:41:05,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
it could prompt Han Gyeol to reconsider,]

646
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:05,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I thought.]

647
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:10,550
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Bearing the hope
of the dual meanings,]

648
00:41:10,550 --> 00:41:12,610
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I gave the photos to him.]

649
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:19,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Don't you have anything
you want to say to me?]

650
00:41:19,220 --> 00:41:21,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's really the end soon.]

651
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:27,230
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hmm...]

652
00:41:33,770 --> 00:41:38,170
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't know
what to say right now.]

653
00:41:38,170 --> 00:41:42,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: My mind is a mess now.]

654
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:46,550
[Kim Han Gyeol: Please give me a moment.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Take your time.]

655
00:41:47,250 --> 00:41:51,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was totally at a loss.]

656
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:56,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hyeok Jin still
expressed his affection to me till the end.]

657
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't expect it.]

658
00:41:58,330 --> 00:42:01,400
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I was overwhelmed by Hyeok Jin]

659
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:02,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: in that moment.]

660
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,670
[Kim Han Gyeol: By his feelings.]

661
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:13,310
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Maybe I'm just not equipped]

662
00:42:13,310 --> 00:42:17,150
[Kim Han Gyeol: to be loved by you.]

663
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:22,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's not like that.
Maybe you're just unsure,]

664
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:27,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: unsure of
what you're equipped of.]

665
00:42:27,290 --> 00:42:34,130
[Kim Han Gyeol: At this moment,
I feel that way.]

666
00:42:34,130 --> 00:42:36,030
[Kim Han Gyeol: I really feel it.]

667
00:42:38,230 --> 00:42:47,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't know
exactly how I'm feeling right now.]

668
00:42:47,580 --> 00:42:52,050
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Tomorrow is the last day.
It's not the end yet.]

669
00:42:53,010 --> 00:42:56,390
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Sort out what's on your mind,]

670
00:42:56,390 --> 00:43:03,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and if you have something to
say or anything else, call me anytime.]

671
00:43:03,860 --> 00:43:06,530
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Whatever it is.]

672
00:43:06,530 --> 00:43:09,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: In the remaining time,
you should say what you want to say, right?]

673
00:43:09,100 --> 00:43:11,670
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

674
00:43:15,640 --> 00:43:19,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I feel better,
but I still want to talk to him more.]

675
00:43:19,440 --> 00:43:25,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: For about 30 minutes,
I felt like I just expressed my perspective]

676
00:43:25,280 --> 00:43:29,950
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and my feelings.
That was a shame.]

677
00:43:29,950 --> 00:43:34,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wanted to hear
his responses to what I said too.]

678
00:43:34,690 --> 00:43:40,430
[Kim Han Gyeol: It was most memorable when
he said I was always the one for him.]

679
00:43:40,430 --> 00:43:44,900
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't expect
someone to be so sure of me.]

680
00:43:44,900 --> 00:43:48,170
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's the first time I felt like
people's hearts can be moved by others.]

681
00:43:49,770 --> 00:43:52,440
[I wavered...]

682
00:43:53,010 --> 00:44:01,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm off. Sort things out
slowly on your own. Take it easy.]

683
00:44:03,650 --> 00:44:05,790
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm leaving. Bye.]

684
00:44:06,550 --> 00:44:11,390
[Can't help feeling regret and guilt...]

685
00:44:11,990 --> 00:44:16,730
[What choice will Han Gyeol make?]

686
00:44:17,260 --> 00:44:21,870
[Expectations and curiosity for the date]

687
00:44:22,070 --> 00:44:28,210
[Who is waiting for Su Min?]

688
00:44:30,980 --> 00:44:34,350
[Kim Su Min: Hello.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hello.]

689
00:44:34,350 --> 00:44:38,120
[Han Gyeol chose Su Min]

690
00:44:38,590 --> 00:44:42,390
[Kim Su Min: Did you wait long?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: No, not long.]

691
00:44:44,560 --> 00:44:50,030
[Kim Han Gyeol: Your outfit's nice.]
[Kim Su Min: Thank you.]

692
00:44:50,030 --> 00:44:54,130
[Kim Su Min: I think
it's the first time we're talking alone.]

693
00:44:54,130 --> 00:44:58,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah, it's fascinating.]

694
00:44:58,240 --> 00:45:01,580
[Kim Su Min: I was shocked
when I got your call yesterday.]

695
00:45:04,250 --> 00:45:07,180
[Kim Su Min: I was very shocked.]

696
00:45:08,020 --> 00:45:13,590
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't tell anyone,
but I've been curious about you.]

697
00:45:14,620 --> 00:45:18,390
[Kim Su Min: I had no idea.]

698
00:45:18,390 --> 00:45:21,630
[Kim Su Min: But when we first met,
you sat in front of me.]

699
00:45:21,630 --> 00:45:25,700
[Kim Su Min: It was comfortable
talking to you while maintaining eye contact.]

700
00:45:27,740 --> 00:45:31,840
[Kim Su Min: And then after all this time,]

701
00:45:31,840 --> 00:45:36,010
[Kim Su Min: I didn't expect
you to call me yesterday.]

702
00:45:36,510 --> 00:45:42,150
[Kim Han Gyeol: I wanted to
sit down and talk with you.]

703
00:45:42,150 --> 00:45:46,520
[Kim Han Gyeol:
It's a bit late, but still...]

704
00:45:46,520 --> 00:45:50,560
[Kim Han Gyeol: I wanted to
go on a date with you, so I called you.]

705
00:45:50,560 --> 00:45:52,560
[Kim Su Min: I see.]

706
00:45:52,830 --> 00:45:55,230
[Kim Su Min: Thank you.]

707
00:45:59,170 --> 00:46:03,510
[Kim Su Min: It's the last day,
and we go home tomorrow.]

708
00:46:03,510 --> 00:46:06,980
[Kim Su Min:
Have you made your final choice?]

709
00:46:08,310 --> 00:46:13,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm about 70% sure.]

710
00:46:13,750 --> 00:46:18,120
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah,
since it's nearing the end.]

711
00:46:18,120 --> 00:46:21,660
[Kim Su Min: 70% is high.]

712
00:46:21,660 --> 00:46:25,930
[Kim Han Gyeol: What about you?]
[Kim Su Min: Me?]

713
00:46:26,760 --> 00:46:31,800
[Kim Su Min: Matters of the heart are tough.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Same for me.]

714
00:46:33,870 --> 00:46:36,610
[Kim Su Min: Matters of the heart are tough.]

715
00:46:37,410 --> 00:46:42,480
[Kim Su Min: Do you have any regrets?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Regrets?]

716
00:46:43,010 --> 00:46:46,420
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't have any regrets.]

717
00:46:46,440 --> 00:46:54,450
[Kim Han Gyeol: I gave my all
in every moment. Really.]

718
00:46:54,450 --> 00:46:56,320
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I have no regrets.]

719
00:46:57,390 --> 00:46:59,850
[Kim Han Gyeol: To make an analogy,]

720
00:46:59,850 --> 00:47:03,830
[Kim Han Gyeol: it was like I've been
on a scary roller coaster,]

721
00:47:03,830 --> 00:47:07,700
[Kim Han Gyeol:
and now I'm nearing the end.]

722
00:47:07,700 --> 00:47:08,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: To make an analogy.]

723
00:47:08,660 --> 00:47:10,670
[Kim Su Min: Right, you kept
saying your dopamine is spiking.]

724
00:47:10,670 --> 00:47:14,000
[Kim Su Min: You told me about that a lot.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I know.]

725
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:19,540
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's like I'm out of breath,
and about to get off soon.]

726
00:47:20,080 --> 00:47:25,980
[Kim Su Min: In my opinion,
out of all the participants,]

727
00:47:26,750 --> 00:47:30,180
[Kim Su Min:
you enjoyed the process the most.]

728
00:47:30,820 --> 00:47:35,820
[The lucky star
who's been on a date since Day One]

729
00:47:36,360 --> 00:47:45,170
[In the process, he's been
hit with countless emotions]

730
00:47:45,430 --> 00:47:47,170
[Kim Su Min: Can I ask you a question?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: What is it?]

731
00:47:47,170 --> 00:47:51,040
[Kim Su Min: You said yesterday's date]

732
00:47:51,040 --> 00:47:54,510
[Kim Su Min: was why you called me.]

733
00:47:55,040 --> 00:47:58,250
[Kim Su Min: What was it exactly?]

734
00:47:58,610 --> 00:48:01,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was curious about you
and wanted to talk to you,]

735
00:48:01,980 --> 00:48:03,850
[Kim Han Gyeol: but we haven't talk much.]

736
00:48:04,360 --> 00:48:07,390
[Kim Han Gyeol: I couldn't just call you,]

737
00:48:07,390 --> 00:48:12,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: so I didn't think much.
But after going on a date with you...]

738
00:48:12,940 --> 00:48:15,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I called you.]

739
00:48:15,620 --> 00:48:19,660
[Kim Su Min: After we had a talk?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

740
00:48:19,660 --> 00:48:26,030
[Kim Su Min: It'd be nice if
we had an active date today.]

741
00:48:26,100 --> 00:48:28,700
[Kim Su Min: But you like the quiet.]

742
00:48:28,700 --> 00:48:29,500
[Kim Han Gyeol: Active dates?]

743
00:48:29,500 --> 00:48:32,660
[Kim Su Min: You said
you liked quiet activities.]

744
00:48:32,660 --> 00:48:35,540
[Kim Su Min: I'm good at remembering
conversations I had with others.]

745
00:48:35,540 --> 00:48:38,420
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Yeah, you have a good memory.]

746
00:48:38,700 --> 00:48:42,260
[Kim Su Min: You said you liked
quiet activities, handicrafts, and taking walks.]

747
00:48:42,260 --> 00:48:44,220
[Kim Su Min: Yes,
you said you liked taking walks.]

748
00:48:44,220 --> 00:48:47,220
[Kim Han Gyeol: I take walks
to clear my mind. But here,]

749
00:48:47,220 --> 00:48:50,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: the more I walk,
the more there is on my mind.]

750
00:48:50,940 --> 00:48:55,110
[Kim Han Gyeol: So taking walks here
isn't refreshing.]

751
00:48:56,460 --> 00:49:00,500
[Kim Han Gyeol: Come to think about it,
there hasn't been a way to refresh here.]

752
00:49:00,950 --> 00:49:03,420
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.
It's rare to get time alone too.]

753
00:49:03,420 --> 00:49:06,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's why I was envious
that you were staying in Block C alone,]

754
00:49:06,080 --> 00:49:08,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: and kept saying
I wanted to visit.]

755
00:49:08,740 --> 00:49:11,900
[Kim Su Min: Were you envious?]

756
00:49:12,380 --> 00:49:14,860
[Kim Su Min: Today is the last date.]

757
00:49:14,860 --> 00:49:18,330
[Kim Su Min:
But it's our first 1-on-1 date.]

758
00:49:19,490 --> 00:49:23,400
[Kim Su Min: There's a lot
we don't know about each other.]

759
00:49:23,400 --> 00:49:26,070
[Kim Su Min: A lot of
conversations to be had.]

760
00:49:27,140 --> 00:49:31,940
[Kim Su Min: It was the last date,
but it felt like a first date.]

761
00:49:32,210 --> 00:49:39,550
[Kim Su Min: There wasn't much rapport.
So he chose me purely out of curiosity.]

762
00:49:39,550 --> 00:49:44,850
[Kim Su Min: It was a date
for Day One or Day Two.]

763
00:49:44,850 --> 00:49:49,660
[Kim Su Min: Having it now
feels a bit too late.]

764
00:49:50,890 --> 00:49:54,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't expect
the date with Su Min]

765
00:49:54,760 --> 00:49:56,000
[Kim Han Gyeol: to be heart-fluttering.]

766
00:49:56,000 --> 00:49:57,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: Like a kind older friend?]

767
00:49:57,300 --> 00:50:02,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: Just having
a relaxing chat with an older friend.]

768
00:50:02,370 --> 00:50:05,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: The chat with Su Min
brought me some comfort.]

769
00:50:05,370 --> 00:50:07,510
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's how I felt.
Just a little bit.]

770
00:50:09,410 --> 00:50:13,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: Now that it's ending,
I'm sort of... relieved?]

771
00:50:13,400 --> 00:50:14,120
[Kim Su Min: Relieved?]

772
00:50:14,420 --> 00:50:17,180
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think I learned a lot
through others,]

773
00:50:17,180 --> 00:50:21,190
[Kim Han Gyeol: about how to
love and be loved.]

774
00:50:21,190 --> 00:50:24,630
[Kim Han Gyeol: I also
learned a lot about myself.]

775
00:50:26,690 --> 00:50:31,900
[Kim Han Gyeol: I can evaluate myself
more objectively from now on.]

776
00:50:36,340 --> 00:50:40,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think
it'll really come in use,]

777
00:50:40,740 --> 00:50:43,380
[Kim Han Gyeol:
even in the tiniest things.]

778
00:50:43,380 --> 00:50:46,610
[Kim Han Gyeol: Anyway,
I have no regrets.]

779
00:50:46,610 --> 00:50:51,120
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was curious about him
and wanted to go on a date with him.]

780
00:50:51,120 --> 00:50:53,650
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I'm happy I got to.]

781
00:50:54,580 --> 00:50:57,380
[Kim Su Min: If I knew
we'd hit it off this well,]

782
00:50:57,380 --> 00:51:01,460
[Kim Su Min: I would've
talked to you more at home.]

783
00:51:01,460 --> 00:51:05,540
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah, I was just so busy.]

784
00:51:06,230 --> 00:51:10,700
[Kim Su Min: You seemed the busiest.]

785
00:51:10,700 --> 00:51:12,630
[Kim Su Min: You were really busy.]

786
00:51:13,340 --> 00:51:18,660
[Kim Su Min: But it's nice to talk like this.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

787
00:51:18,920 --> 00:51:23,180
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I'm glad I got to talk to you.]

788
00:51:23,180 --> 00:51:28,000
[Kim Su Min: At home,
if there's time, let's talk more.]

789
00:51:28,000 --> 00:51:29,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: Let's do that.]

790
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:30,780
Bye.

791
00:51:30,160 --> 00:51:36,460
[Su Min and Han Gyeol's date
ends with both regret and relief]

792
00:51:37,520 --> 00:51:39,580
[Cho Yun Jae: Did Min Seong go out too?]

793
00:51:39,580 --> 00:51:41,450
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I think so.]
[Cho Yun Jae: He's not here.]

794
00:51:41,450 --> 00:51:44,160
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I guess
Min Seong didn't choose me.]

795
00:51:45,660 --> 00:51:46,900
[Cho Yun Jae: What? Really?]

796
00:51:46,900 --> 00:51:50,190
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm here,
but Min Seong went out.]

797
00:51:50,190 --> 00:51:52,400
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, I know.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who is it?]

798
00:51:52,400 --> 00:51:54,570
[Cho Yun Jae: Isn't it Taichi?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I don't know.]

799
00:51:54,570 --> 00:51:56,260
[Cho Yun Jae: Taichi isn't home either.]

800
00:51:55,780 --> 00:51:56,300
Really?

801
00:51:56,260 --> 00:51:58,740
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Maybe it's Taichi.]
[Cho Yun Jae: There's no one in Block A now.]

802
00:51:58,740 --> 00:52:02,900
[Lee Hyeong Jun: They sleep in the same room.
I guess feelings developed.]

803
00:52:03,580 --> 00:52:06,680
[Cho Yun Jae: Doesn't look like it.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You never know.]

804
00:52:06,680 --> 00:52:08,310
[Cho Yun Jae:
There's nothing to worry about.]

805
00:52:08,310 --> 00:52:10,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Oh, really?]

806
00:52:10,820 --> 00:52:12,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You never know.]

807
00:52:13,220 --> 00:52:15,890
[Cho Yun Jae:
But I don't think you need to worry.]

808
00:52:14,420 --> 00:52:15,380
Yeah?

809
00:52:15,890 --> 00:52:20,430
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm hungry.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Eat something.]

810
00:52:20,430 --> 00:52:23,090
[Kim Sun Wook: There's nothing to eat, right?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Aren't there dumplings?]

811
00:52:23,090 --> 00:52:25,760
[Kim Sun Wook: Dumplings?]

812
00:52:29,330 --> 00:52:31,570
[Cho Yun Jae: Don't you feel like drinking?]

813
00:52:31,570 --> 00:52:33,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why? Do you become
a different person after drinking?]

814
00:52:33,820 --> 00:52:35,770
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I thought so.]

815
00:52:35,770 --> 00:52:40,910
[Cho Yun Jae: I become very happy.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why? Are you unhappy now?]

816
00:52:40,910 --> 00:52:42,210
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Because
things aren't going your way?]

817
00:52:42,210 --> 00:52:44,320
[Cho Yun Jae: No, no.]

818
00:52:44,320 --> 00:52:46,580
[Cho Yun Jae: It's awkward after all.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah?]

819
00:52:46,580 --> 00:52:49,090
[Cho Yun Jae: Hyun Jun and I
are not awkward.]

820
00:52:49,090 --> 00:52:53,360
[Cho Yun Jae: But Sun Wook seems awkward
with me, so I'm uncomfortable.]

821
00:52:53,360 --> 00:52:56,790
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sun Wook
is simpler than you think.]

822
00:52:56,790 --> 00:53:00,230
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't think he's simple.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He is.]

823
00:53:01,670 --> 00:53:03,530
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's because
you're emotion-based.]

824
00:53:03,530 --> 00:53:06,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sun Wook's totally logic-based.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I see.]

825
00:53:06,340 --> 00:53:10,270
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He thinks Hyun Jun
belongs to him anyway.]

826
00:53:10,270 --> 00:53:12,140
[Cho Yun Jae: That's what I thought
at the beginning.]

827
00:53:12,140 --> 00:53:15,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really?]
[Cho Yun Jae: That's why I didn't do anything.]

828
00:53:15,680 --> 00:53:17,020
[Cho Yun Jae: I want to turn back time.]

829
00:53:17,280 --> 00:53:19,950
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why?]
[Cho Yun Jae: I should've been more proactive.]

830
00:53:19,950 --> 00:53:25,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Oh, not to change targets?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

831
00:53:25,460 --> 00:53:28,530
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What a man.]

832
00:53:28,530 --> 00:53:31,430
[Cho Yun Jae: Are you a woman?]

833
00:53:31,430 --> 00:53:34,630
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No wonder.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Stop.]

834
00:53:34,630 --> 00:53:37,040
[Cho Yun Jae: Did they choose each other?]

835
00:53:37,040 --> 00:53:39,240
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Huh?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Maybe Taichi chose Min Seong.]

836
00:53:39,240 --> 00:53:40,200
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who knows?]

837
00:53:40,200 --> 00:53:43,210
[Cho Yun Jae: Even if
Min Seong didn't choose Taichi.]

838
00:53:44,010 --> 00:53:46,740
[Cho Yun Jae: It doesn't matter to you, right?
You don't care, right?]

839
00:53:46,740 --> 00:53:48,420
[Cho Yun Jae: You're not worried at all.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But Min Seong]

840
00:53:48,420 --> 00:53:50,110
[Lee Hyeong Jun: can choose two people.]

841
00:53:50,110 --> 00:53:53,650
[Cho Yun Jae: Then he might choose Taichi,
after this date.]

842
00:53:53,650 --> 00:53:57,320
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes, you never know.
They sleep together every day.]

843
00:53:59,720 --> 00:54:02,590
[Kim Sun Wook:
Should we start with the dumplings?]

844
00:54:02,590 --> 00:54:05,200
[Kim Sun Wook: Oh,
there are only dumplings.]

845
00:54:05,200 --> 00:54:07,930
[Kim Sun Wook:
I should've microwaved it first.]

846
00:54:07,930 --> 00:54:10,130
[Lee Hyun Jun: To thaw it?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

847
00:54:10,130 --> 00:54:13,940
[Lee Hyun Jun: Done.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Thank you.]

848
00:54:16,540 --> 00:54:18,110
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was nothing.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hmm?]

849
00:54:18,110 --> 00:54:20,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was nothing.]

850
00:54:24,800 --> 00:54:26,300
[Kim Sun Wook: It's hot.]

851
00:54:26,300 --> 00:54:27,730
[Lee Hyun Jun: Hot!]
[Kim Sun Wook: Is it hot?]

852
00:54:27,730 --> 00:54:30,400
[Kim Sun Wook: Is it hot?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Ah! It's so hot.]

853
00:54:30,400 --> 00:54:32,000
[Kim Sun Wook: Is it too hot?]

854
00:54:32,000 --> 00:54:33,700
[Lee Hyun Jun: Ah, so hot!]

855
00:54:33,700 --> 00:54:35,740
[Kim Sun Wook: I didn't expect it
to be so hot.]

856
00:54:35,740 --> 00:54:38,280
[Kim Sun Wook: It's so small,
so I thought it wasn't that hot.]

857
00:54:42,280 --> 00:54:45,580
[Lee Hyun Jun: I almost teared up.]

858
00:54:47,380 --> 00:54:50,150
[Lee Hyun Jun: Let's eat dumplings.]

859
00:54:53,920 --> 00:54:58,430
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sit here.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Why?]

860
00:54:58,430 --> 00:54:59,830
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
So they can eat face to face.]

861
00:54:59,830 --> 00:55:01,370
[Cho Yun Jae: I was
going to sit next to you.]

862
00:55:03,270 --> 00:55:05,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It looks a bit burnt.]

863
00:55:05,440 --> 00:55:07,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: Really? It's good burnt.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah?]

864
00:55:12,910 --> 00:55:14,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Mm.]

865
00:55:14,580 --> 00:55:17,180
[Kim Sun Wook: Is it cooked?]

866
00:55:17,980 --> 00:55:22,190
[Lee Hyun Jun: He said they were burnt.]
[Kim Sun Wook: What's wrong?]

867
00:55:22,190 --> 00:55:24,720
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
"He said they were burnt?"]

868
00:55:24,720 --> 00:55:26,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why'd you tell on me?]

869
00:55:26,460 --> 00:55:29,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's OK. It's good.]

870
00:55:29,660 --> 00:55:32,600
[Kim Sun Wook: When are you going out?]

871
00:55:32,600 --> 00:55:35,130
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Maybe I'm not going out.]

872
00:55:35,130 --> 00:55:38,270
[Cho Yun Jae: Congratulations.]

873
00:55:36,500 --> 00:55:37,560
Congratulations?

874
00:55:38,270 --> 00:55:41,940
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Congratulations?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Get some rest.]

875
00:55:41,940 --> 00:55:46,210
[Kim Sun Wook: Don't you want some rice?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Kimchi stew?]

876
00:55:50,610 --> 00:55:55,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Come to think about it,
Hyun Jun ranked all three of us high.]

877
00:55:57,890 --> 00:56:00,360
[Kim Sun Wook: Right.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: In his top ranks.]

878
00:56:00,590 --> 00:56:03,290
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He must be
excited to eat with us.]

879
00:56:04,630 --> 00:56:06,860
[Cho Yun Jae: Tell him to pay for it.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Pay for it?]

880
00:56:06,860 --> 00:56:10,230
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He's cooking for us.]

881
00:56:12,540 --> 00:56:13,820
Thank you.

882
00:56:18,340 --> 00:56:21,690
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hyun Jun, how do you feel,
eating with your ideal types?]

883
00:56:21,690 --> 00:56:23,050
[Cho Yun Jae: You have to pay for it.]

884
00:56:23,060 --> 00:56:24,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You ranked us all high.]

885
00:56:24,340 --> 00:56:26,530
[Lee Hyun Jun: How much do I have to pay?]

886
00:56:26,540 --> 00:56:27,700
[Cho Yun Jae: 50,000 won per hour?
(~35 USD)]

887
00:56:28,320 --> 00:56:30,980
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's expensive.]

888
00:56:34,940 --> 00:56:36,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Don't you think
this group of us is funny?]

889
00:56:36,820 --> 00:56:39,090
[Kim Sun Wook: Why?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I think it's funny.]

890
00:56:39,090 --> 00:56:40,890
[Kim Sun Wook: Is it funny?]

891
00:56:45,300 --> 00:56:49,800
[Hyun Jun and Sun Wook cooks together,
and then cleans up together]

892
00:56:50,570 --> 00:56:51,900
[Cho Yun Jae: Where are you going?]

893
00:56:51,900 --> 00:56:53,970
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm jealous.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'll be back.]

894
00:56:53,970 --> 00:56:56,640
[Cho Yun Jae: Have fun.]

895
00:56:57,440 --> 00:57:04,120
[After Hyeong Jun leaves,
Yun Jae returns to Block A]

896
00:57:14,890 --> 00:57:17,730
[Kim Sun Wook: I think
Min Seong really likes him.]

897
00:57:17,730 --> 00:57:19,060
[Lee Hyun Jun: Hyeong Jun?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

898
00:57:19,060 --> 00:57:20,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why do you say that?]

899
00:57:20,770 --> 00:57:25,240
[Kim Sun Wook: He always comes here.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It seems that way.]

900
00:57:25,240 --> 00:57:27,670
[Kim Sun Wook: So I just leave the room.]

901
00:57:27,670 --> 00:57:29,610
[Kim Sun Wook: When it's my room.]

902
00:57:29,610 --> 00:57:33,210
[Kim Sun Wook: I envy him.]

903
00:57:41,220 --> 00:57:45,090
[Lee Hyun Jun: When can we go out?]
[Kim Sun Wook: I know, right?]

904
00:57:45,090 --> 00:57:46,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: Will it be the three of us?]

905
00:57:46,690 --> 00:57:49,890
[Kim Sun Wook: Which three?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yun Jae, you, and I.]

906
00:57:49,890 --> 00:57:50,620
[Kim Sun Wook: I see.]

907
00:57:50,620 --> 00:57:51,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: Will the three of us
go out together?]

908
00:57:51,960 --> 00:57:55,970
[Kim Sun Wook: The three of us together?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I feel like it is.]

909
00:57:58,900 --> 00:58:01,710
[Lee Hyun Jun: What's wrong?]

910
00:58:01,710 --> 00:58:04,810
[Kim Sun Wook: Interesting.]

911
00:58:04,810 --> 00:58:07,380
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think it is.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

912
00:58:07,380 --> 00:58:11,680
[Kim Sun Wook: But it's the last date.
The last date.]

913
00:58:11,680 --> 00:58:14,950
[Kim Sun Wook: Nothing wrong with some fun.]

914
00:58:16,020 --> 00:58:18,690
[Kim Sun Wook: It'll be fun.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: You sure?]

915
00:58:18,690 --> 00:58:21,530
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

916
00:58:27,930 --> 00:58:28,730
[Kim Su Min: Go in. Hurry.]

917
00:58:32,800 --> 00:58:35,940
[Cho Yun Jae: It was a time
when we could play without worries.]

918
00:58:35,940 --> 00:58:39,010
[Kim Sun Wook: It was a time
when I saw everyone smile the most.]

919
00:58:39,010 --> 00:58:41,210
[Kim Su Min: What a feast for the eyes.]

920
00:58:41,210 --> 00:58:43,410
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It was really fun.]

921
00:58:43,410 --> 00:58:47,120
[Going all out for the last night]

922
00:58:43,740 --> 00:58:46,660
-Wifi! -Cheers!

923
00:58:49,290 --> 00:58:50,620
[Kim Su Min: I had a great time.]

924
00:58:54,790 --> 00:58:56,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: It should be a good memory.]

925
00:58:57,490 --> 00:59:00,230
[Making memories together,
and...]

926
00:59:01,330 --> 00:59:05,670
[Cho Yun Jae: Can I choose someone?
Do I have to choose someone?]

927
00:59:05,670 --> 00:59:08,510
[Taichi: I thought a lot myself.]

928
00:59:08,510 --> 00:59:10,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: A choice
so as to leave no regret.]

929
00:59:10,770 --> 00:59:13,410
[Oh Min Seong:
Relieved that it's finally over,]

930
00:59:13,410 --> 00:59:15,220
[Oh Min Seong: and now
I have no more worries.]

931
00:59:15,220 --> 00:59:17,180
I still like him.

932
00:59:17,220 --> 00:59:19,180
[Kim Su Min: I'll be true to my feelings.]

933
00:59:19,180 --> 00:59:22,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I've been
thinking about what to say.]

934
00:59:23,190 --> 00:59:25,320
[Thank you, really…]

935
00:59:25,590 --> 00:59:28,620
[Kim Sun Wook: I had a great time too,
thanks to you, hyung.]

936
00:59:29,230 --> 00:59:32,800
[In the last moment, can everyone
say goodbye with a smile?]
